  <preface xml:id="preface">
    <title>How to Use These Notes</title>

    <p>
      These notes are a <term>guided</term> handout: most
      pages contain blanks (<m>\underline{\hspace{2em}}</m>)
      and worked examples whose final lines are left empty
      on the student copy.  We will fill in these gaps
      together during class.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Each set of notes is a <term>worksheet</term>
      covering one class meeting's worth of material.
      Bring the worksheet for the day, a pencil, and a
      fresh stack of patience.
    </p>
  </preface>
